node.text: GUYS! I MADE A BURGER!!! SO excited to share what I’ve created for #theburgershowdown with @lightlifefoods Plant-Based Burgers. Order the “Triple S (Sarah’s Southwestern Smash)” on @ubereats in LA and vote for it today on theburgershowdown.com. I hope you love it as much as I do! The Burger Showdown will be supporting and raising donations for Frontline Foods in their mission to bring revenue into local restaurants, while helping to feed the heroes working on the frontlines. @lightlifefoods @offthemenu @theburgershowdown @delilah #ad

node.text: Always trying to multitask 🙃 I’ve teamed up with @Rooted_Rituals #ad because healthy hair starts with a healthy scalp. As a transplant patient (and #spoonie 🙋🏻‍♀️), I’ve suffered side effects like hair loss, but these products can change the game. I love using their Cooling and Strengthening Tonic with their Scalp Massager (literally can’t put it down), it stimulates circulation and helps me have a healthy scalp. The BEST part of this partnership is that Rooted Rituals and I are donating $10,000 to @FeedingAmerica to help during this pandemic. You can find the full line of @Rooted_Rituals exclusively @walmart. #rootcrew #rootedrituals

node.text: To say you’re my best friend just isn’t enough. I am so lucky to have found my soul sister (YES, I KNOW IT’S CHEESY!) in you. I love watching us grow in to the capable, limitless, and strong women we are. I wouldn’t be standing here today if it wasn’t for you @ciaracrobinson and for that, I am eternally grateful. I can’t wait for our future together at the lake house! Co-faux daddies activated! HAPPY BIRTHDAY MY FOREVER WOMAN!!!! 💋💋💋💋

node.text: I was not educated on the subject of Juneteenth in school. I learned as an adult. I continue to educate myself on matters surrounding the systemic racism of our country, and I hope for a day where all children are taught the true history of our past.
